        {
          "field_name": "fee_waiver_condition",
          "candidate_value": "\u00a7\u00a7 Members of your family \u2013 including spouses, parents, children and siblings (and their immediate family) \u2013 benefit from a tiered fee rate scale.",
          "value_type": "string",
          "confidence": 0.55,
          "extraction_method": "heuristic_text",
          "source_document_id": "src-rbc-pdf-fa650b9c0caac5c3",
          "source_snapshot_id": "snap-2ee16ae54829be04",
          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-564d1e3c98d35492",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "\u00a7\u00a7 Designed to help you and your family members across Canada reduce overall investing costs.\n\u00a7\u00a7 When you and/or your family have combined assets of $250,000 or more invested in this account, you can\nstart benefiting from a lower fee rate.*\n\u00a7\u00a7 Fee rates decrease for the entire family as your combined assets grow.\n\u00a7\u00a7 Members of your family \u2013 including spouses, parents, children and siblings (and their immediate family) \u2013\nbenefit from a tiered fee rate scale.\nRBC\n\u00ae\nINVESTMENT ADVANTAGE ACCOUNT\nFamily matters \u2013\nBuild your wealth together\nYou You & Partner You, Partner,\nSibling & ChildrenYou , Partner & Sibling You, Partner, Sibling,\nChildren & Parents\n*Applies to mutual fund investments only.\nLower your account fee rate as your assets grow\nAssets\nAccount fee rate",
